    "en": {
      "title": "Investigations about the power cut when the Prime Minister's house was burnt down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The chairman of the commission, Mr. Janaka Ratnayake, said that the Public Utilities Commission will conduct a formal investigation to reveal the truth about the power cut when a group set fire to Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's private residence at Fifth Lane, Colombo 7.",
        "The chairman further said that there was no plan to turn off the electricity in the Colombo area yesterday (9) after 6 pm."
      ],
